  "detailed_description": "FurBalls Racing is a fast-paced, platforming racing game that's silly and surprisingly challenging! Whether you want to have a party with friends or try to get perfect runs on every stage, FurBalls Racing is fun for all kinds of players!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1962490/extras/3365827fcdb2014bdcf632c1cb9747e5.poster.avif?t=1744580444\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1962490/extras/3365827fcdb2014bdcf632c1cb9747e5.webm?t=1744580444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1962490/extras/3365827fcdb2014bdcf632c1cb9747e5.mp4?t=1744580444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as over a dozen unique squishy FurBalls, each one with different attributes!<br></li><li>Roll, wall jump, spin drift, and take creative shortcuts as you rush towards the finish line!<br></li><li>Eat cheese, then use it to... shoot poop?... at your opponents...<br></li><li>Play locally with up to four players in split screen!<br></li><li>Race against up to fifteen CPU players in Grand Prix!<br></li><li>Record and face your own best times as ghosts in Time Trials mode, where you can also race against challenging staff ghosts!<br></li><li>Try to get medals on every stage to unlock more playable characters!<br></li><li>Play online to race against distant friends or anyone else!<br></li><li>Challenging unlockable content, secrets, crazy shortcuts, and hidden advanced game mechanics for speedrunners and other hardcore players!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "FurBalls Racing is a fast-paced, platforming racing game that's silly and surprisingly challenging! Whether you want to have a party with friends or try to get perfect runs on every stage, FurBalls Racing is fun for all kinds of players!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1962490/extras/3365827fcdb2014bdcf632c1cb9747e5.poster.avif?t=1744580444\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1962490/extras/3365827fcdb2014bdcf632c1cb9747e5.webm?t=1744580444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1962490/extras/3365827fcdb2014bdcf632c1cb9747e5.mp4?t=1744580444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as over a dozen unique squishy FurBalls, each one with different attributes!<br></li><li>Roll, wall jump, spin drift, and take creative shortcuts as you rush towards the finish line!<br></li><li>Eat cheese, then use it to... shoot poop?... at your opponents...<br></li><li>Play locally with up to four players in split screen!<br></li><li>Race against up to fifteen CPU players in Grand Prix!<br></li><li>Record and face your own best times as ghosts in Time Trials mode, where you can also race against challenging staff ghosts!<br></li><li>Try to get medals on every stage to unlock more playable characters!<br></li><li>Play online to race against distant friends or anyone else!<br></li><li>Challenging unlockable content, secrets, crazy shortcuts, and hidden advanced game mechanics for speedrunners and other hardcore players!</li></ul>",
